"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-2024-03-13-peyton-manning-host-nbc-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-broadcast\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The post-NFL career of Peyton Manning has forayed into a successful tenure in media.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 84, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23, \"end\": 37, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peyton_Manning\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Peyton Manning\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peyton_Manning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peyton_Manning\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But even for someone as accomplished as Manning, his latest venture is a prominent next step.\", \"from\": 86, \"to\": 179, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Manning is set to join NBC\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Mike Tirico in Paris this summer to help anchor the network\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s coverage of the Olympic opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 181, \"to\": 317, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 212, \"end\": 223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tirico\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mike Tirico\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tirico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tirico\"}, {\"begin\": 227, \"end\": 232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999995853500827, \"rank\": 4.1464997752348584e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Manning won\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t be the only prominent sidekick to Tirico on the broadcast.\", \"from\": 318, \"to\": 392, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"NBC also will have Grammy Award-winning singer Kelly Clarkson as part of the network\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s television coverage of the ceremony.\", \"from\": 393, \"to\": 518, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 393, \"end\": 396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.8959210304857352, \"rank\": 0.1146943319452149, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 412, \"end\": 418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grammy_Awards\", \"score\": 0.9999999962635684, \"rank\": 2.3929617602485946e-09, \"text\": \"Grammy\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grammy_Awards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grammy_Awards\"}, {\"begin\": 440, \"end\": 454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kelly Clarkson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The trio announced the news onThe Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon\\u00c2\\u00a0on Tuesday night.\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 606, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Manning also spoke withAndrew Marchand ofThe Athletic\\u00c2\\u00a0about how the arrangement came about, mentioning that Tirico first began courting him for the role last May at the Kentucky Derby.\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 778, \"end\": 792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kentucky_Derby\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.448231255672872e-16, \"text\": \"Kentucky Derby\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kentucky_Derby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kentucky_Derby\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI kind of argued with him as to why he and NBC thought I was worthy,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Manning told Marchand.\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 892, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 841, \"end\": 844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.8959210304857352, \"rank\": 0.1146943319452149, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cHe said they were bringing in Kelly Clarkson to kind of give the perspective of the fan and wanted me to share the perspective of what these athletes are thinking about it.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  As for Tirico, he was thrilled he was able to convince both Manning and Clarkson to join the telecast.\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 1175, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 926, \"end\": 940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kelly Clarkson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\"}, {\"begin\": 1145, \"end\": 1153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremy_Clarkson\", \"score\": 0.999999794206836, \"rank\": 1.709360864589969e-07, \"text\": \"Clarkson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremy_Clarkson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremy_Clarkson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI couldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t be more thrilled that they both said yes,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Tirico told Marchand.\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1259, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Manning has been a staple during ESPN\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099sMonday Night Football\\u00c2\\u00a0telecasts over the past couple seasons, as he hosts an alternate\\u00c2ManningCastbroadcast\\u00c2\\u00a0with brother Eli.\", \"from\": 1261, \"to\": 1429, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Manning also leads\\u00c2Omaha Productions, a company that has a close partnership with ESPN.\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1517, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1512, \"end\": 1516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"score\": 0.999999999994543, \"rank\": 4.707894711023047e-12, \"text\": \"ESPN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even in the context of Manning\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s accomplished media career, this summer\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Olympics coverage might be Manning\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s most significant role yet.\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1662, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The opening ceremony of the Paris Olympics is scheduled for July 26.\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1732, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Loading recommendations...\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1760, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please wait while we load personalized content recommendations  Mike McDaniel is a staff writer on the Breaking and Trending News team at Sports Illustrated, where he has worked since January 2022.\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1958, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1825, \"end\": 1838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_McDaniel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mike McDaniel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_McDaniel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_McDaniel\"}, {\"begin\": 1899, \"end\": 1917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2386059072458226e-20, \"text\": \"Sports Illustrated\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His work has been featured at InsideTheACC.com, SB Nation, FanSided and more.\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 2036, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2007, \"end\": 2016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SB_Nation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"SB Nation\", \"types\": []